@Kayoku @aselle @gargn I encountered exactly the same issue when using toco (or python code directly) to convert an existing frozen protobuf

toco \
  --output_file ../data/mobile.tflite \
  --graph_def_file ../data/frozen_inference_graph.pb \
  --output_format TFLITE \
  --inference_type FLOAT \
  --inference_input_type FLOAT \
  --input_arrays image_tensor --input_shapes 1,-1,-1,3 \
  --output_arrays num_detections,detection_boxes,detection_scores,detection_classes
